10 phases, each w/ testable deliverable:
  - Ph 0-1: Foundation + text chat (Groq API) — reuse my_ai patterns                                                                                            
  - Ph 2: Tool system — "Alice, open Chrome" → Chrome opens
  - Ph 3-4: Voice in (Faster-Whisper) + voice out (Edge-TTS) — full voice loop
  - Ph 5: Speaker verification — Alice obeys only you
  - Ph 6: Tauri desktop UI — glassmorphism chat app (~50MB RAM)
  - Ph 7: Trigger sequences — double clap = Iron Man boot
  - Ph 8: Bilingual EN/JA w/ subtitles
  - Ph 9-10: Memory/learning + polish

  ~6-8 weeks of focused sessions. ~635MB RAM on laptop → fits 8GB.

  Review the plan file — has full tech stack table, architecture diagram, project structure, feasibility notes, and reusable code paths.

