 ---
 Architecture

 ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
 │                    ALICE SYSTEM                       │
 │                                                       │
 │  [Audio Listener — Process 1]                        │
 │   Mic → Clap Detect / Wake Word / VAD / Speaker ID  │
 │   → STT (Faster-Whisper) → text                     │
 │          │                                            │
 │          │ multiprocessing.Queue                      │
 │          ▼                                            │
 │  [Core Brain — Process 2]                            │
 │   Text → LLM Router (Groq/Ollama)                   │
 │   → Tool System (PC ctrl, files, web, news, weather) │
 │   → TTS (Edge-TTS/Piper) → Speaker                  │
 │   → Memory (SQLite)                                  │
 │          │                                            │
 │          │ WebSocket (localhost)                       │
 │          ▼                                            │
 │  [Tauri UI — Process 3]                              │
 │   Chat log + Voice viz + Status + Settings           │
 │                                                       │
 │  [System Tray — pystray]                             │
 │   Background service, hotkey, auto-start             │
 └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

