 Answer: Is This Doable?

 Yes. 100% doable with you and Claude. The hardest parts (LLM, STT, TTS) are solved by mature libraries. Chester already has working AI chat code in my_ai. The
  reference projects provide proven patterns. The 10-phase plan ensures each step has a working deliverable before moving to the next. Total estimated
 timeline: ~6-8 weeks of focused sessions.


 To run right now (needs Groq API key):
  1. Copy .env.example → .env
  2. Set GROQ_API_KEY=your_key (free at console.groq.com)
  3. py -3.14 alice/main.py → chat with Alice in terminal, she can check system stats, list files, fetch PH news